model_has_permissions
________________________________________
📌 MEMBUAT FILE .env
🚀 1. BUAT FILE .env
Buat file:
.env
di root project.
________________________________________
🚀 2. ISI FILE .env
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=
